---
import '../styles/global.css';
import Layout from './layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <section class="space-y-4">
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Alex Gaudon, a software developer focused on building web applications.
    </p>
    <p>
      I currently build software for risk management professionals at
      <a
        href="https://www.clearrisk.com"
        class="text-blue-400 hover:underline"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >ClearRisk</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here you'll find some of my
      <a
        href="/projects"
        class="text-blue-400 hover:underline"
      >projects</a>
      and thoughts on technology
      <span class="text-stone-400 italic">(maybe a blog someday)</span>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Come chat with me at the weekly
      <a
        href="https://ctsnl.ca/"
        class="text-blue-400 hover:underline"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >CTSNL</a>
      meetups:
      <span class="text-stone-300">Thursdays @ 7:00pm, Jumping Bean, Elizabeth Ave.</span>
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>